                    </p>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-heading font-bold">JS</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-white font-bold font-heading uppercase">Jana Svobodová</h4>
